{"tid":2328583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西半山賓士花園首度有住戶染疫","createTime":"2020-12-16T15:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T18:42:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a56a0f237f8bb92b33e00df70b9f6261e78bb03","tid":2328583,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T15:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5Go3AIxyT.eJc9h6lQoOLQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-12/367b1c70-3e91-11eb-bdd7-93f71c6d7e07\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F5Go3AIxyT.eJc9h6lQoOLQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-12%2F367b1c70-3e91-11eb-bdd7-93f71c6d7e07&h=ab262a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第4波疫情持續，衞生防護中心昨晚(14日)更新確診者住宅及到訪過的大廈名單，當中位於西半山的賓士花園首次有住戶染疫，而昨日的82宗確診個案中，有29人報稱居於公共屋邨。另外，確診者曾到訪的食肆方面，新增兩間食肆上榜，包括油塘鯉魚門廣場的明星海鮮酒家，以及上環街市及熟食中心。<br />\n<br />\n根據衞生防護中心資料，中西區西半山的賓士花園首度有人確診，患者為一名73歲男患者(編號7565)，屬本地相關個案。另有29人稱居於公共屋邨，包括慈雲山慈正邨、油塘油麗邨、東涌逸東(二)邨等。"},{"pid":"5d03696895afb37b741eb5346a9c4fecc3d42a7d","tid":2328583,"uid":340088,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T15:41:42.000Z","msg":"有錢人真係開心"},{"pid":"1667a585f58c7a372c8ebbfacb5b7406bb32cc6c","tid":2328583,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T15:57:52.000Z","msg":"上環個熟食中心好似中撚左好多次啦喎"},{"pid":"36fac05a9b1792ea4a8134b86450bac6d969442a","tid":2328583,"uid":300006,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T17:10:41.000Z","msg":"富者⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"60340c88583cf38fec6252c850df800527cc0d32","tid":2328583,"uid":82394,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1667a585f58c7a372c8ebbfacb5b7406bb32cc6c","tid":2328583,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T15:57:52.000Z","msg":"上環個熟食中心好似中撚左好多次啦